### CareCore API - REST Client
### VS Code REST Client Extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# After login, paste your token below:
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
@refreshToken = YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN
# ─────────────────────────────────────────


### ══════════════════════════════
###  AUTH
### ══════════════════════════════

### 1. Register Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@carecore.com",
  "password": "Admin1234",
  "full_name": "System Admin",
  "role": "admin"
}


### 2. Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@carecore.com",
  "password": "Admin1234"
}


### 3. Get Current User (Me)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 4. Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refresh_token": "{{refreshToken}}"
}


### ══════════════════════════════
###  HOMES
### ══════════════════════════════

### 5. Create Home
POST {{baseUrl}}/entities/Home
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "data": {
    "name": "Sunrise House",
    "type": "24_hours",
    "address": "12 Oak Street, London",
    "postcode": "E1 6RF",
    "team_leader_id": "PASTE_STAFF_ID_HERE",
    "status": "active"
  }
}


### 6. Get All Homes
GET {{baseUrl}}/entities/Home
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ══════════════════════════════
###  RESIDENTS
### ══════════════════════════════

### 7. Create Resident
POST {{baseUrl}}/entities/Resident
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "data": {
    "display_name": "Alice M.",
    "home_id": "PASTE_HOME_ID_HERE",
    "risk_level": "low",
    "status": "active",
    "placement_type": "childrens_home"
  }
}


### 8. Get Active Residents
GET {{baseUrl}}/entities/Resident?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}